01:31.000 --> 01:34.330
Let's think of a biased estimator to explain that point.

01:34.660 --> 01:40.030
What if somebody told you that you will have to find the average height of Americans by taking a sample

01:40.300 --> 01:43.860
finding its mean and then adding one foot to that result.

